Author: GitHub
Title: A look at the open source zone at GitHub Universe
Description:
GitHub Universe is back, and the Open Source Zone is where the real magic happens. Get a sneak peek at the coolest hacker fair for developers, where maintainers bring their projects to life. This year, we're featuring projects like Homebrew, Oh My Zsh, OpenCV, Pixijs, and many more.

Digital passes are free! Get yours now at https://githubuniverse.com
